c("\xa0Expanded\xa0and\xa0improved\xa0<span id = "word">Education</span>\xa0coverage\xa0and\xa0measurement\xa0of\xa0learning\xa0outcome. While\xa0school\xa0enrollment\xa0rates\xa0in\xa0Myanmar\xa0are\xa0relatively\xa0high,\xa0completion\xa0rates\xa0lag\xa0behind\xa0the\xa0country\x92s\xa0peers.\xa0 <span id = "word">Education</span>,\xa0especially\xa0in\xa0rural\xa0areas,\xa0had\xa0historically\xa0been\xa0underfunded,\xa0and\xa0this\xa0has\xa0exacerbated\xa0inequalities,\xa0as\xa0 poorer\xa0and\xa0more\xa0isolated\xa0areas\xa0comparatively\xa0lack\xa0financial\xa0means\xa0and\xa0technical\xa0capacity. \xa0Increased\xa0access\xa0to\xa0 basic\xa0<span id = "word">Education</span>\xa0has\xa0the\xa0potential\xa0to\xa0play\xa0a\xa0critical\xa0role\xa0to\xa0ensuring\xa0<span id = "word">Inclusive</span>\xa0growth.\xa0\xa0The\xa0Government\xa0is\xa0working\xa0 to\xa0increase\xa0retention\xa0rates,\xa0and\xa0IDA\xa0investments\xa0to\xa0support\xa0reform\xa0of\xa0basic\xa0<span id = "word">Education</span>\xa0will\xa0focus\xa0on\xa0improving\xa0 and\xa0expanding\xa0Myanmar\x92s\xa0existing\xa0school\xa0grants\xa0and\xa0targeted\xa0student\xa0stipends\xa0programs\xa0as\xa0part\xa0of\xa0this\xa0effort,\xa0 as\xa0well\xa0as\xa0on\xa0the\xa0implementation\xa0of\xa0professional\xa0development\xa0programs\xa0for\xa0township\xa0and\xa0school\xa0officials\xa0and\xa0 periodic\xa0early\xa0grade\xa0reading\xa0assessments.\xa0The\xa0operations\xa0will\xa0support\xa0reforms\xa0through\xa0(i)\xa0expanding\xa0the\xa0 coverage\xa0of\xa0the\xa0stipend\xa0program\xa0and\xa0improving\xa0operational\xa0mechanisms\xa0for\xa0targeting\xa0poor\xa0and\xa0vulnerable\xa0 students\xa0which\xa0would\xa0improve\xa0retention,\xa0(ii)\xa0improving\xa0the\xa0reliability\xa0and\xa0transparency\xa0of\xa0the\xa0school\xa0grants\xa0 scheme;\xa0and\xa0(iii)\xa0building\xa0the\xa0capacity\xa0of\xa0the\xa0Ministry\xa0of\xa0<span id = "word">Education</span>,\xa0townships,\xa0schools\xa0and\xa0communities\xa0to\xa