c("\xa0Increased\xa0productivity\xa0in\xa0farming\xa0<span id = "word">and</span>\xa0agribusiness\xa0 \xa0 . Half\xa0of\xa0Myanmar\x92s\xa0poor\xa0depend\xa0on\xa0agriculture\xa0for\xa0their\xa0livelihoods,\xa0<span id = "word">and</span>\xa0agricultural\xa0productivity\xa0is\xa0low,\xa0mostly\xa0 due\xa0to\xa0poor\xa0rice\xa0yields\xa0compounded\xa0by\xa0an\xa0over?dependence\xa0on\xa0rice.\xa0Low\xa0yields\xa0in\xa0turn\xa0are\xa0a\xa0result\xa0of\xa0a\xa0lack\xa0of\xa0 access\xa0by\xa0farming\xa0households\xa0to\xa0improved\xa0agricultural\xa0assets,\xa0infrastructure\xa0<span id = "word">and</span>\xa0services.\xa0More\xa0productive\xa0 agriculture\xa0would\xa0also\xa0encourage\xa0job\xa0creation\xa0through\xa0agro?processing\xa0<span id = "word">and</span>\xa0trading\xa0activities.\xa0The\xa0World\xa0Bank\xa0 aims\xa0to\xa0increase\xa0agricultural\xa0productivity\xa0in\xa0order\xa0to\xa0have\xa0a\xa0positive\xa0effect\xa0on\xa0agricultural\xa0incomes.\xa0The\xa0World\xa0 Bank\xa0expects\xa0to\xa0support\xa0an\xa0integrated\xa0program\xa0that\xa0combines\xa0improvements\xa0in\xa0<span id = "word">Irrigation</span>\xa0<span id = "word">and</span>\xa0<span id = "word">Drainage</span>,\xa0 extension\xa0services,\xa0<span id = "word">and</span>\xa0value\xa0chain\xa0upgrades\xa0to\xa0increase\xa0crop\xa0yields\xa0<span id = "word">and</span>\xa0develop\xa0a\xa0competitive\xa0rural\xa0sector\xa0that\xa0 offers\xa0opportunities\xa0to\xa0all\xa0rural\xa0households.\xa0\xa0Alongside\xa0analytical\xa0work,\xa0these\xa0initial\xa0engagements\xa0will\xa0pilot\xa0new\xa0 approaches,\xa0inform\xa0the\xa0policy\xa0dialogue\xa0<span id = "word">and</span>\xa0serve\xa0a\xa0demonstration\xa0effect\xa0to\xa0facilitate\xa0reform\xa0across\xa0the\xa0sector.\xa0\xa0 The\xa0 World\xa0 Bank\xa0 will\xa0 also\xa0 support\xa0 further\xa0 agricultural\xa0 productivity\xa0 enhancements\xa0 by\xa0 providing\xa0 agrometeorological\xa0 services,\xa0 facilitating\xa0 inl<span id = "word">and</